{"tid":2030782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暗指支持川普的非裔「不是黑人」 拜登挨轟道歉","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T03:13:50.000Z","uid":28765,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c53d83346c52eb98c3b7e79ab9c7a5d917ee7091","tid":2030782,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:01:22.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國前副總統、民主黨總統候選人拜登（Joe Biden）21日接受一名著名的非裔電台主持人訪問時暗指，支持總統川普的非裔美國人「不是黑人」，引發大量的攻擊聲浪，拜登隨後也出面道歉。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，拜登的「非黑人」（ain't black）言論引起共和黨人員以及非裔社區的批評，部分社運人士則提醒拜登，即使非裔美國人多數不支持川普，拜登仍需要討好非裔選民，拜登22日也道歉表示，自己不應該故作聰明。<br />\n<br />\n拜登曾在前總統歐巴馬（Barack Obama）任內擔任8年的副總統，在爭議性的發言後，拜登道歉表示，自己絕不會將非裔美國人的選票視為理所當然，並補充，沒有人應該基於種族、宗教或背景投票給任何政黨。<br />\n<br />\n電台主持人查拉曼（Charlamagne tha God）在訪問中詢問拜登，是否會選擇一名非裔女性擔任副總統，拜登提到，多名非裔女性都在考慮的名單內，拜登的競選團隊一度試圖結束採訪。<br />\n<br />\n在查拉曼試圖向拜登提出其他問題時，拜登回答，「若你仍無法決定自己將支持拜登或川普，那麼你不是黑人」。查拉曼的節目「早餐俱樂部」（Breakfast Club）是全國性的節目，每個月有超過800萬聽眾。<br />\n<br />\n在拜登公開道歉之前，川普的競選團隊與媒體進行了視訊記者會。共和黨非裔參議員史考特（Tim Scott）表示，拜登的的言論令他震驚，傲慢自大且種族歧視。史考特推文表示，2016年的總統大選已有130萬名非裔選民投票支持川普，但拜登卻告訴這些選民，他們不是黑人。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的顧問桑德絲（Symone Sanders）則推文表示，拜登一生都在為非裔社區努力，訪問中的言論都只是玩笑，拜登只是希望將自己為非裔社區的付出和川普做出區別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3174784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3174784&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=400b404c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3174784&h=a2b98bd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3174784</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-52773555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-52773555&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=ad6589d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-52773555&h=0325ac40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-52773555</a>"},{"pid":"2726cbe7fb22c5652df5e9ef8ceb7db41d9fdc8f","tid":2030782,"uid":173179,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"Not my nigga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64873d83af75ffb924fbca5f122fa884efd3cbf","tid":2030782,"uid":15812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:06:28.000Z","msg":"全部進化晒變白人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796599af9750b13b8125735fe13f0c3081fb0f12","tid":2030782,"uid":42364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"左媒開始夾佢幫拜登洗白啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知佢係咪畀人恐嚇要改口"},{"pid":"f2281f536110004ecffffd9f922f2348a5c10943","tid":2030782,"uid":20170,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"Hillary係咁，China joe都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本心底裡最撚racist"},{"pid":"a370c3f884e0d155394f1a3bf0f36772ea77cda3","tid":2030782,"uid":24814,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zvyJz8dEeLs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzvyJz8dEeLs&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=b49d7a44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zvyJz8dEeLs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nYgVo9-iF-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnYgVo9-iF-c&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=7ffe693f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nYgVo9-iF-c</a><br />\n的確智商高過白左"},{"pid":"835da6ddf8835f72296204e2b3441aec1b5587db","tid":2030782,"uid":137569,"like":5,"dislike":0